  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"2.8.6\" data-text=\"Version 2.8.6\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 2.8.6</h3>\n<p>September 18, 2024</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.lifecycle:lifecycle-*:2.8.6</code> is released. Version 2.8.6 contains <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/1923636d71735aa7f25cd267a3ef7adc2e6af530..68c770fd5ee88b093114c4361b9cc2cd3c436bb7/lifecycle\">these commits</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>The <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">NullSafeMutableLiveData</code> Lint error has improved support for smart casts, avoiding false positives. (<a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+/85fed6d07668f2e903172592580d8076cb6da80a\">85fed6</a>, <a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/181042665\">b/181042665</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Dependency Updates</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Lifecycle Runtime Compose now depends on <a href=\"/jetpack/androidx/releases/compose-runtime#1.7.1\">Compose Runtime <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">1.7.1</code></a></li>\n</ul>",
